overview: Josh, Quinn, Kent, Harper, and Trey jet off to London and Prague to take in the sights, do some exploring, and enjoy winter in these amazing cities, while making sure to enjoy plenty of each other as well. Whether it’s to warm each other up or their simply getting caught up in the excitement of fun and fascinating trip abroad, five of Corbin Fisher’s most popular studs end up having some of the most intense, sweatiest, raunchiest, most cum-soaked sex we’ve ever seen.
title: European Stimulus
